      <h2>Safety Profile</h2>
      <p>Among the 54 patients who received REGENECYTE, 7% (n=4) had an infusion reaction based on 388 voluntary reports. This compares to 65.4% of infusions with any-grade reactions in the COBLT study (442 infusions).</p>

      <!-- AE butterfly chart -->
      <div class="chart-box">
        <div class="chart-title">Infusion-Related Adverse Events</div>
        <div class="chart-sub">COBLT (442 infusions) vs REGENECYTE (54 patients)</div>
