      <div class="side-card"><h4>Collaborating Centers</h4><ul class="side-list"><li>City of Hope</li><li>Mayo Clinic</li><li>UCLA Medical Center</li><li>Stanford Hospital</li><li>Duke University</li><li>Children&rsquo;s Hospital LA</li><li>Mt. Sinai Medical Center</li></ul></div>
